186397.「ただいまより 第６回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加する:
We are pleased to introduce you to the
beautiful women who will be participating in
the 6th Astoltia Queen Contest!

186398.「総勢４８人の予選を勝ち抜いた 上位５名と\n ファルパパ神による特別推薦枠 ３:
The top 5 winners from the 48 qualifiers, plus 3 specially recommended by Falpapa God, will compete against each other for the top 8
beauties!

186399.「予選通過者は 以上の５名になります。\n 最後に ファルパパ神による 特別推薦:
These are the five qualifiers. Lastly, there are 3 specially recommended by Falpapa God! This time, we have three special nominees from
Ethene Kingdom!

186400.「まず ご登場いただくのは こちらの美少女！\n 天使の歌声で 聴く者を涙させる:
First of all, we would like to introduce you to this beautiful girl! She is a miracle diva with an angelic singing voice that brings
tears to the eyes of those who listen to her!

186401.「月夜に咲いた ラウラの花……\n エテーネの歌姫 シャンテ！:
Laura's flower bloomed in the moonlit night
Shante, the diva of Ethene!

186402.「王都キィンベルから 来ました。\n こんな盛大なステージに立てて 幸せ……。\:
I am from Royal City Kimbel. I am happy to be
on such a big stage. I want to send this
feeling to everyone.

186403.「それでは 聴いてください……\n 心を込めて 歌います。\n コンテスト会場の:
Now, please listen to me as I sing with all my
heart.  A song dedicated to the contestants

186405.「シャンテの美声を\n ここで聴かせるのは もったいないだろっ！\n クイーンに:
Shante's beautiful voice is too good to be
heard here! Let's wait until she becomes
queen! What?

186407.「でも 歌いたい気持ちは 変わらないの。\n クイーンになったら きっと歌を届け:
But my desire to sing will never change. When
I become the queen, I will surely deliver my
songs, so please support me!

186408.「気を取り直して……お次は その歌姫の姉！\n 王都キィンベルの 気高き錬金術師:
Now let's get back on track with the diva's sister! The noble alchemist of the Royal City Kimbel has even managed to alchemize the
number of votes!

186409.「イケメンな性格で あこがれる女性も急増中！？\n 妹愛なら 誰にも負けない……:
The number of women who admire his handsome personality is increasing rapidly! When it comes to sisterly love, no one can beat Linka,
the alchemist of brilliance!

186410.「いいか お前ら！\n あたしのことは いいから\n とにかく 妹のシャンテを:
Listen, guys! Don't worry about me, just
support my sister Shante, okay?

186411.「……だけど まあ\n あたしに 投票してくれたなら\n それは それで うれし:
But if you voted for me, that would make me
happy.

186412.「本年度の大トリは このお方だ！\n エテーネ王宮に咲いた 一輪の高貴なバラ！\:
This year's grand finale is this man! A single noble rose blooming at the Ethene Royal Palace! Despite her innocent appearance, she
is a tomboy!

186413.「遥かなる旅路は どこへと続くのか！？\n 時をかける王女 メレアーデ！:
Where will your journey lead you? Mereade, the
princess of time!

186414.「ふふっ。なんだか 楽しそうなイベントね。\n やるからには いちばんを目指すわ:
Hmmm. Sounds like a fun event. If we're going
to do this, we're going to be the best! Let's
have a wonderful time together!

186415.「私が クイーンになる未来へ……\n みんなの応援で 連れていってね！:
Please take me to the future where I will
become a queen with your support!

186416.「……以上 ８名の美女たちが \n クイーンの座をかけて コンテストを争います。:
These eight beauties will compete for the
title of queen.

186417.「果たして 栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will be crowned with glory? It is you who
will decide!

186418.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n 今回も選りすぐりの美女が そろいました。\n:
What do you think ? We have a great selection of beauties for you to choose from this time. Did you find your favorite
one?

186419.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n その方のチョコ作りを 手伝っ:
If you decide on a beautiful woman who you
think is worthy of being queen, please help
her make the chocolates.

186420.「あなたが チョコ作りを手伝った相手に\n あなたの１票が 投じられるのです。\:
Your vote will go to the person you helped
make the chocolates. Please think carefully
before you make your choice.

186421.「選び終わりましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
When you have finished your selection, please
stop by my place for a chat. I'll be outside.

186422.「ただいまより 第６回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発表:
We will now announce the results of the 6th
Astoltia Queen Contest!

186423.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who will be the queen of the Chocolat Fontenay
Castle? The result will finally be revealed!

186424.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！:
Ladies and gentlemen! Please pay attention to
the stage!

189792.「まずは 前大会の覇者が 堂々の登場だ！\n ４回目の出場で ついに 勝ち取った:
First of all, the champion of the previous tournament made a grand entrance! This is the fourth time he has participated in this
tournament, and he has finally won the crown! Will they be able to win the unprecedented consecutive championships?

189793.「今のは ベホマではない ホイミだ！\n アストルティアの青き導き手……セラフィ:
Now that's not BehoMa, that's Heal! Seraphi,
the blue guide of Astoltia!

189794.「えへへ。前回は たくさんの声援ありがとう。\n やっと クイーンになれたよー！:
Hehe. Thanks for all the cheers last time. I
finally became a queen! Everyone, let's aim
for first place again this time!

189795.「全国のマイラーよッ！ 準備はいいかッ！？\n 強い！ 優しいッ！ 美しいッッ！:
All mylars nationwide! Are you ready? Strong!
Gentle! Beautiful! Our heroine is here!

189796.「戦いの時は 来た！\n 初代 アストルティア・クイーン！\n オーガニック ビ:
The time for battle has come! The first
Astoltia Queen! Ogre Nick Beauty Maille!

189797.「今こそ 修行の成果を見せる時……！\n 誰であろうと 手かげんしないわ！\n:
Now is the time to show the results of your training! I won't hold back, no matter who you are! Come on, come at me from wherever you
are!

189798.「ふたつの世界の友好を結ぶため\n 未来を見つめる うるわしの女神官。\n だが:
The Uruwashi no Onna Priest stares into the future in order to forge a friendship between the two worlds. But look at the face of the
pretty girl she suddenly reveals!

189799.「ナドラガンドとの 美しき架け橋！\n 竜の世界の正統派ヒロイン エステラ！:
A beautiful bridge to Nadragand! Estella is a
legitimate heroine of the dragon world!

189800.「皆さんの 期待に応えるため\n 今回は 私自身の意思で 参りました。\n ここ:
I came here of my own volition this time to
live up to your expectations. I am happy to be
here.

189801.「アストルティアの すべての皆さんに\n 笑顔を届けられるよう 精一杯 がんばり:
I will do my best to bring smiles to everyone
in Astoltia. Please accept my sincerity!

189802.「また今年も この人が やってきた！\n いにしえの塔で真実を追う 辺境の考古学:
This person has come again this year! Will the Frontier Archeologist, chasing true fruit in an ancient tower, unlock the missing link to
glory?

189803.「ヒストリカ イズ 場違い感……\n いやいや それどころか 立派な優勝候補だ！:
Historica is out of place. No, no, no, on the contrary, it's a great candidate for the championship! Everyone's friend of the heart,
Historica!

189804.「イケる……！ 今年こそ イケる……！ \n 見えるぞっ 栄冠への道筋が！\n:
I can do it! I can do it this year!I can see
the road to glory! Queen! How sweet that
sounds!

189805.「ノーモア・かませドッグ！\n 私が優勝して 歴史に新たなる１ページを\n 刻ん:
No more kamasedogs! I'm going to win this
thing, and I'm going to write a new page in
history! And for that, give-me-a-vote!

189806.「何度 非情な運命に 打ちひしがれようと\n 決して あきらめずに 立ちあがる…:
No matter how many times we are doomed to a
cruel fate, we will never give up, we will
rise up. Because! Because HER is a Hero!

189807.「今年こそ！ 悲願の勝どきを見せてやれッ！\n 純潔のバトルプリンセス 勇者姫ア:
This is the year! Show them the victory
they've been longing for! Pure
battlePurineSeth Hero Princess Anlucia!

189808.「厳しい戦いになることは わかってる……！\n けれど どんな大きな困難だって\:
I know it's going to be a tough fight! But no
matter how big the challenge, we can overcome
it with your support!

189809.「伝説の勇者の 誇りにかけて……\n 最後まで 正々堂々と 戦い抜くわ。\n さ:
I'm proud to be a legendary Hero and I'm going
to fight fair and square until the end. This
is the year we win the title of Queen!
